    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just never stops. no matter what meds i take or how much rest i get, the burning in my legs is just... always there. i feel like i've been fighting this for years and there's no finish line. i'm just so tired of being in a body that feels like a cage of pain. it feels so unfair that i have to keep waking up to this every single day.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
